{"tid":469803,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家上次食煙係幾時？點解會唔再食？","createTime":"2017-11-15T16:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T17:00:23.000Z","uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f24bd4319a62042ef5387b847e4c35c41f439484","tid":469803,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"都成半年無食煙，上次個女性朋友同我講，食煙對身體唔好，食小d啦，之後我就無食，但我見到你食噃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec0df0c0e0dcfecac3367126ec6cc03249dd11d","tid":469803,"uid":54581,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"3秒前<br />\n<br />\n決心介煙"},{"pid":"1858281162c17e44cdc80052d644d526838d7588","tid":469803,"uid":61415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"吸煙危險健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe197606a0e6a04d99849ac20261fe197eee043","tid":469803,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3秒前<br />\n<br />\n決心介煙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭好難介，不過d煙咁貴，我多數痴煙食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18a55e87cd402e33a9d953243822104f16d3cc7","tid":469803,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吸煙危險健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天氣一冬成班打完邊爐飲好多酒就好想食架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef6d3d3a952012578863ec38cf4d2ac0adff187","tid":469803,"uid":36054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最近係咁咳 要食藥所做暫時無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc85931193cb338f9b12966db1143717ab638a63","tid":469803,"uid":154227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"7年無食過，放低果刻就無左食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef0559de6672bbab626d2ad2a694625fffb0657","tid":469803,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"原本兩年幾冇食<br />\n前排炒車，個人呆呆下咁買左包嚟定驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尋日開始重新戒，今日一支都冇食"},{"pid":"d520f269f89c8b8bf5ad2285275d4f758c7cd585","tid":469803,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最近係咁咳 要食藥所做暫時無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好番記得食番啦。"},{"pid":"87a68cae24a59bc7387f47e496137606f59a7d89","tid":469803,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7年無食過，放低果刻就無左食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都幾難，如果有班狗友食煙，一齊玩好難唔食。"},{"pid":"362fb1d81caf60032197a96eb057bdd0ea062f36","tid":469803,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"食到身體差而且成身都一陣味 身邊既人都唔好受 嗱嗱聲戒咗佢最好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然好辛苦但有堅定意志去戒就會成功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戒緊嗰時千祈唔好諗住食一支半支應酬吓無事 如果唔係就等於又返返轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a0fcf876760f56e3608cfd71edbf979c800651","tid":469803,"uid":132227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最近係咁咳 要食藥所做暫時無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喉嚨痛+咳一定要食<br />\n一嘢那落去不知幾爽<br />\n唔食唔知身體好呀"},{"pid":"004a205034853a58b67b6b0d2e302fe2a3a0da34","tid":469803,"uid":71144,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"有個人妻同我講食一淡<br />\n食到就食成世食唔到就唔好食<br />\n我吸左一淡雖然無咩感覺<br />\n但係內心個種責備感令我覺得反胃<br />\n最後我話以後唔再食到依家<br />\n<br />\n當時21歲去大陸KTV陪人唱K<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我知我係好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4d14c5bb9dedc58481dae5f4a2984b9f98ae66","tid":469803,"uid":144480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"9個月前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被朋友勸唔好食"},{"pid":"7fdf1c5c97a319b02c8e78cee4976dd94ba505b9","tid":469803,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"幾年前，本身冇癮，出黎做野之後就冇食"},{"pid":"984230f1d88be334142724a32598f83e697d3f46","tid":469803,"uid":146769,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"大家上次食煙係幾時？<br />\n頭先食完晏<br />\n<br />\n點解會唔再食？<br />\n因為夠鐘番office"},{"pid":"9ff4664e1e24c1bde9720dafc51535fdc973f3a4","tid":469803,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:49:01.000Z","msg":"個幾月前 好想唔再食"},{"pid":"59f633887804690f6341a70b1da220a65070b2d5","tid":469803,"uid":121393,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"北上叫雞先會買<br />\n香港太撚貴"},{"pid":"f2cd55497ca9b33f3dc7ed052137f8e4e1baa406","tid":469803,"uid":156318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:11:08.000Z","msg":"兩分鐘前<br />\n每次都同自己講食埋今日就唔再食<br />\n但都係忍唔住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 